results.name: Order of Fibonacci group F(n,3) (or 0 if the group is infinite).
comment: A column of the array described in A202624. See that entry for references.
maple: f:=n-> if n mod 3 = 0 then n-1 elif n mod 3 = 1 then n^3-1 else 0 fi; # Gives all values correctly except that a(2) should be 8.
